data.description: Built in 2022, welcome to this delightful farmhouse inspired gem in the heart of Magnolia Green & just steps away from Moseley Elementary! The aesthetic of this home is both rustic & chic as you are welcomed by barnwood columns on your full front porch, board & batten siding & a stylish metal awning. Open the custom front door to find an airy office w rich LVP flooring & functional built-ins, ideal for homework too! The open-concept living rm boasts LVP flooring & recessed lighting leading you to the sunny kitchen/morning rm. Cook like a pro in the luxurious kitchen complete w granite counters/tile backsplash, an oversized island w bar seating, gas cooking, SS appliances, W/I pantry & pendant/recessed lighting. HW steps lead you to an expansive primary suite flaunting a distinct tray ceiling, plush carpeting, CF, W/I closet & luxury bath. 3 additional bdrms offering large closets & CF's plus an upstairs laundry round out the 2nd floor. Enjoy a 10x14 deck for the grill master, 2 car garage, fenced backyard & irrigation. MAGNOLIA GREEN HAS AN ARRAY OF UNBEATABLE AMENITIES TO INCLUDE AN AQUATIC CENTER, WALKING PATHS, CHAMPIONSHIP GOLF, SOCIAL ACTIVITIES, TENNIS & A FARMERS MARKET.
